  "detailed_description": "<h1>DISCORD</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429540/extras/ce312ae9ba209044264b74d4153b08fe.avif?t=1765973662\" width=615 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Craft. Relax. Repeat. A cozy puzzle-builder where every tile breathes life.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Build a living mosaic — where settlers chat, animals play, and your choices ripple across a world that feels alive. No battles, no stress… just endless zen creativity. Until your kingdom sings… or crumbles. Then rebuild, better.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429540/extras/746863e6983e5746896c005595477339.poster.avif?t=1765973662\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429540/extras/746863e6983e5746896c005595477339.webm?t=1765973662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429540/extras/746863e6983e5746896c005595477339.mp4?t=1765973662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429540/extras/5d34cee30b4961158065f77c13642371.avif?t=1765973662\" width=615 height=100 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🧩 Puzzle Meets Playground</strong><br>Like meditative construction set for adults. Simple rules (match forest-to-forest, water-to-water), but endless possibilities. 15+ unique buildings, 30+ hand-crafted tiles, zero pressure.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🎨A Canvas, Not a Grid</strong><br>Paint world with freeform tools! <i>Your settlers — your audience!</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>✨Art:</strong> Vibrant, tactile textures — sky you want to <i>watch</i>, trees that sway like dancers, villages with mismatched chimneys.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🌌 Sound:</strong> Lofi beats mixed with nature ASMR (crackling fires, owl hoots, the <i>click</i> of perfectly placed tiles).</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>When Perfectionism Falters... Unleash a Meteor Storm! 💥</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"Harmonis: Where even collapse is art. Build masterpieces... or turn chaos into fireworks! 🌟\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429540/extras/7798028021c57d3b42fcecf1dafa4c19.poster.avif?t=1765973662\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429540/extras/7798028021c57d3b42fcecf1dafa4c19.webm?t=1765973662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429540/extras/7798028021c57d3b42fcecf1dafa4c19.mp4?t=1765973662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429540/extras/ce312ae9ba209044264b74d4153b08fe.avif?t=1765973662\" width=615 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Craft. Relax. Repeat. A cozy puzzle-builder where every tile breathes life.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Build a living mosaic — where settlers chat, animals play, and your choices ripple across a world that feels alive. No battles, no stress… just endless zen creativity. Until your kingdom sings… or crumbles. Then rebuild, better.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429540/extras/746863e6983e5746896c005595477339.poster.avif?t=1765973662\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429540/extras/746863e6983e5746896c005595477339.webm?t=1765973662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429540/extras/746863e6983e5746896c005595477339.mp4?t=1765973662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429540/extras/5d34cee30b4961158065f77c13642371.avif?t=1765973662\" width=615 height=100 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🧩 Puzzle Meets Playground</strong><br>Like meditative construction set for adults. Simple rules (match forest-to-forest, water-to-water), but endless possibilities. 15+ unique buildings, 30+ hand-crafted tiles, zero pressure.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🎨A Canvas, Not a Grid</strong><br>Paint world with freeform tools! <i>Your settlers — your audience!</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>✨Art:</strong> Vibrant, tactile textures — sky you want to <i>watch</i>, trees that sway like dancers, villages with mismatched chimneys.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🌌 Sound:</strong> Lofi beats mixed with nature ASMR (crackling fires, owl hoots, the <i>click</i> of perfectly placed tiles).</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>When Perfectionism Falters... Unleash a Meteor Storm! 💥</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"Harmonis: Where even collapse is art. Build masterpieces... or turn chaos into fireworks! 🌟\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429540/extras/7798028021c57d3b42fcecf1dafa4c19.poster.avif?t=1765973662\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429540/extras/7798028021c57d3b42fcecf1dafa4c19.webm?t=1765973662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429540/extras/7798028021c57d3b42fcecf1dafa4c19.mp4?t=1765973662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
